ight. hope this helps.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Feb  6 06:38:36 2004</em></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br> 'Valdon Gravedancer' Terris-Thule. Dwarven Cleric 34th circle.<br> 'Junglebug Sugarpants' Terris-Thule. Halfling Druid. 51st season.<br> 'Shinook Eldergod' Terris-Thule. Troll Shaman of 32nd rite.<br> 'Soultree Vixen' Terris-Thule. Woodelf Ranger of 34th season.</td></tr>
